text: Vikas Gupta is an Indian politician from Fatehpur, Uttar Pradesh, affiliated with Bhartiya Janata Party. He is member of the Uttar Pradesh Legislative Assembly, elected in 2017. ==References== Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:Members of the Uttar Pradesh Legislative Assembly Category:Bharatiya Janata Party politicians from Uttar Pradesh Category:Uttar Pradesh MLAs 2017–
